      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>When you reach 14th level, you partake some of the true secrets of the Undying. On your turn, you can use a bonus action to regain hit points equal to [[/r 1d8]] + your warlock level. Additionally, if you put a severed body part of yours back in place when you use this feature, the part reattaches.</p><p>Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a short or long rest.</p></div>",
